3. Golden Visa
- 10-year residency for investors, specialized professionals, and exceptional talent.
- Family members eligible for residency linked to main visa.

4. Business & Trade License
- Annual renewal required; tenancy contract (Ejari) needed.
- Initial approval, trade name reservation, office lease required for new setup.